messageBody:
Leila wrote:

> Thanks,
>
> dumpKeys() helped. But I do not know why the key
> looks like the following:
>
> quad_[Lcom.mydomain.Node;_int_int
>

[LXXX; is Java bytecode's way of saying "Array".

So [Ljava.lang.String; means "Array of java.lang.String"
